 VGM Example E04
 Exporting geometry from Root to XML
 --------------------------------------
 
 Source: Root tutorial rootgeom.C macro
         Main program rootgeom.cxx
         
 1. The provided installation script (E03/install.sh)
    will install rootgeom.cxx main program:
    ./install.sh
    
    This step is not necessary if you installed all examples
    at once from up directory.
  
 2. Your environment for VGM has to be set first, see doc/INSTALL)
    
 3. Run example
    ./rootgeom
 
 4. Open and view the generated XML files;
    in GraXML:
    graxml
    w.show("TOP.agdd");
    w.show("TOP.gdml");

                
